additional_info:
Oct 2014: initial version.

You might want to add another style clause like this:

#gb > div > div:nth-child(1) > div:nth-child(1) {
  display: none;
}

Please note the clause above hides non-gplus objects in case you are using non-gplus-linked gmail accounts.

css:
@-moz-document domain(mail.google.com) {

#gb > div > div:nth-child(1) > div:nth-child(2)> div:nth-child(4) {
  display: none;
}

#gb > div > div:nth-child(1) > div:nth-child(2)> div:nth-child(3) {
  display: none;
}

}
